TIP: Leave "Fields" blank to export a full product record with dynamic headers. 
To specify header fields, specify product attributes separated by commas or
newslines, leave no whitespace 
e.g. "zoovy:prod_name,zoovy:base_price,zoovy:prod_image1" (without the quotes) - 
without specifying which fields you want to export you will be limited to 500 products per export.
